{
  "stem": "2833.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] he was in the-- [SIGHS] we had our own, what they called ghetto police.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But the ghetto police was really more to keep order amongst us, not to-- you know, they were-- had nothing to do with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the only thing that they were strict about was stealing in kitchens or in the bakery or wherever food was used to-- and made, you know, cooked or baked or whatever.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my husband was one of those that of police to, to watch over that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I worked after that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After I had come back from planting the trees, I worked in the so-called transport commission, which was the office which put the transport to the east together because nobody said Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't even know for sure where it's going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was called transport to the east.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were certain rules that, you know, the people that worked for the Germans were not allowed to go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The people that we needed to run the ghetto were not allowed to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So you had to kind of always, you know, try to find people that were not connected to any of that and put them in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was a horrible job because, you know, you, you wanted to help one person, and you had to put somebody else in for it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it's just there had to be 1,000 people ready to go within three days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we worked day and night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it got, it got very, very tough.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I got sick for a while and had to-- had something on my lungs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so I wasn't allowed to walk around.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
